{
  "texts": [
    "Flux comparison between eRASS1 and 4XMM catalogues.",
    "The upper panel displays the 0.2-2 keV fluxes of point sources.",
    "The brightest sources with at least 5σ flux measurements are plotted in red points with green 1-sigma uncertainties.",
    "The other sources are plotted in blue points without error bars.",
    "The black lines indicate 1:1 and deviation from 1:1 by a factor of 2."
  ]
}